TITLE: Creating Monster Object in Rust
DESCRIPTION: Creates a Monster object in Rust using the FlatBuffers builder. It sets various properties like position, mana, hp, name, inventory, color, weapons, and equipment.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/flatbuffers/blob/master/docs/source/tutorial.md#2025-04-16_snippet_81

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
let orc = Monster::create(&mut builder, &MonsterArgs{
    pos: Some(&Vec3::new(1.0f32, 2.0f32, 3.0f32)),
    mana: 150,
    hp: 80,
    name: Some(name),
    inventory: Some(inventory),
    color: Color::Red,
    weapons: Some(weapons),
    equipped_type: Equipment::Weapon,
    equipped: Some(axe.as_union_value()),
    path: Some(path),
    ..Default::default()
});
```

