TITLE: Serializing Data with FlatBuffers in C++
DESCRIPTION: C++ code snippet demonstrating how to use FlatBufferBuilder to serialize a Monster object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/flatbuffers/blob/master/docs/source/quick_start.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: cpp
CODE:
```
#include "flatbuffers.h"
#include "monster_generated.h"

int main() { 
  // Used to build the flatbuffer
  FlatBufferBuilder builder;

  // Auto-generated function emitted from `flatc` and the input 
  // `monster.fbs` schema.
  auto monster = CreateMonsterDirect(builder, "Abominable Snowman", 100);

  // Finalize the buffer.
  builder.Finish(monster);
}
```

