TITLE: Reading FlatBuffer Binary File in Go
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to read a FlatBuffer binary file in Go. It imports necessary packages, reads the binary file into a byte slice, and uses the generated GetRootAsMonster function to access the data.
