TITLE: Using Object-Based API with FlatBuffers in Dart
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the object-based API for FlatBuffers in Dart, which allows for unpacking a FlatBuffer into objects for easier manipulation, and then packing it back into a FlatBuffer.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/flatbuffers/blob/master/docs/source/languages/dart.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
