TITLE: Serializing Vector of Tables in Go
DESCRIPTION: Creates a FlatBuffer vector by prepending weapon offsets in reverse order. Uses MonsterStartWeaponsVector and EndVector methods.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/flatbuffers/blob/master/docs/source/tutorial.md#2025-04-16_snippet_41

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
// Create a FlatBuffer vector and prepend the weapons.
// Note: Since we prepend the data, prepend them in reverse order.
sample.MonsterStartWeaponsVector(builder, 2)
builder.PrependUOffsetT(axe)
builder.PrependUOffsetT(sword)
weapons := builder.EndVector(2)
```

