TITLE: Adding Precompiled Headers to Targets in FlatBuffers CMake Build
DESCRIPTION: Defines a function to add precompiled headers to build targets when using CMake 3.16 or newer. For non-MSVC compilers, it excludes src/util.cpp from precompiled header processing.
