TITLE: Configuring and Installing pkg-config File for FlatBuffers in CMake
DESCRIPTION: Generates and installs a pkg-config file for FlatBuffers when either the shared or static library is built.
SOURCE: https://github.com/google/flatbuffers/blob/master/CMakeLists.txt#2025-04-16_snippet_29

LANGUAGE: CMake
CODE:
```
if(FLATBUFFERS_BUILD_SHAREDLIB OR FLATBUFFERS_BUILD_FLATLIB)
    configure_file(CMake/flatbuffers.pc.in flatbuffers.pc @ONLY)
    install(
      FILES "${CMAKE_CURRENT_BINARY_DIR}/flatbuffers.pc"
      DESTINATION ${CMAKE_INSTALL_LIBDIR}/pkgconfig
    )
endif()
```

